# ── Secrets & tokens — NEVER commit these ──────────────────────────────────────
**/config/enctoken.json
**/config/enctoken.json.bak
**/config/credentials.json
**/config/credentials.json.local
**/.env
**/.env.*

# ── Logs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.log.bak
**/logs/
**/bot.log
**/bot.log.bak
**/token_refresh.log

# ── Historical data CSVs (large, downloaded fresh by the bot) ──────────────────
**/data/daily/
**/data/weekly/

# ── Python compiled / cache ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# ── Backup / copy files (use git for versioning, not filename copies) ─────────
*- Copy.*
*- Copy/
* - Copy.*

# ── OS / editor noise ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── Playwright debug screenshots (uploaded as Actions artifacts instead) ──────
/tmp/kite_debug_*.png
/tmp/kite_debug_*.html
